# uniswapv3-sdk-uint256 — Project Architecture

## Overview

Go port of the [Uniswap V3 SDK](https://github.com/Uniswap/v3-sdk) (TypeScript), forked from [daoleno/uniswapv3-sdk](https://github.com/daoleno/uniswapv3-sdk) and **rewritten for performance** with `holiman/uint256` instead of `math/big`.

- **Module:** `github.com/bobinmad/uniswapv3-sdk-uint256`
- **Go version:** 1.24
- **License:** MIT (upstream daoleno)

The project is used as a library by an external **simulator** (`irq/common/simulator/unimath`) — API changes (especially `SwapResultV2`, `StepFeeResult`, `Pool.Swap`) can break downstream consumers.

---

## Package Layout

```
constants/    — Factory address, fee tiers, tick spacings, Q96/Q192, ZeroU256/OneU256
entities/     — Pool, Route, Trade, Position, Tick, TicksHandler
utils/        — All V3 math: FullMath, SqrtPriceMath, TickMath, SwapMath, uint256 ops
periphery/    — Calldata encoders: SwapRouter, Quoter, NFT PM, Staker, Permit, Payments
examples/     — Runnable demos (quoter, swap, liquidity) + generated contract bindings
```

---

