## Key Entities

### Pool (`entities/pool.go`)

```go
type Pool struct {
    Address, Token0, Token1, Fee, SqrtRatioX96, Liquidity, TickCurrent, TickSpacing
    TickDataProvider *TicksHandler
    // embedded calculators + scratch buffers
}
```

Constructors: `NewPoolV2` (standard), `NewPoolV3` (simulation-style with `Address`, `initTick`). `NewPool` is deprecated (`big.Int` API).

### Trade / Route (`entities/trade.go`, `entities/route.go`)

Multi-route trades with `ExactIn`/`ExactOut`, `BestTradeExactIn`/`Out`, `PriceImpact`.

### Position (`entities/position.go`)

Liquidity position with `CalcAmount0`/`CalcAmount1`, mint/burn amounts with slippage.

